parameters:
\SE[9]Ah, I finally managed to catch up with you...
\!\SE[8]I'm sorry... I ended up being late...

\SE[3]Unagi-chan...! \SE[1]I'm glad... I was worried about
you...!

\SE[4]However... the gatekeeper here, Alice, is quite
formidable as expected. \SE[3]I think it would be better for
you to step back.

\SE[16]That's right... If it's just Unagi-chan, they might
die easily...

\SE[20]I...I was thinking the same thing... \!\SE[1]So, I
brought a substitute helper instead...!

\SE[7]Hey, Nagi. I came here because you asked me to...
\SE[44]But I didn't agree to help these guys.

\SE[5]Oh, was that bad...? \!\SE[21]I'm sorry... I didn't
have anyone else to rely on... \!\SE[0]If it seems too
difficult, should I go back?

\SE[32]...Hmph. I can't afford to be underestimated. \.This
is nothing worth considering.

\SE[17]Yaiyai! You always show up in unexpected places!
\SE[15]Are you actually aiming for something...!?

\SE[47]I couldn't care less about your expectations.
\!\SE[0]I'm not free either. Let's quickly finish this job.

\SE[2]I am a person who follows through on what I say. I
said I would help Lunaroa, didn't I? \SE[1]...Now then,
let's quickly begin the trial.

\SE[5]...Okay, I understand. \!\SE[1]Then, I'll unlock the
final seal...

\SE[14]That is not Lunaroa-san! \SE[13]It is probably an
illusion created based on memories... The final guardian...!
